773
00:58:35,750 --> 00:58:37,920
Where will you go?

774
00:58:37,950 --> 00:58:40,120
I won't let you

775
00:58:40,360 --> 00:58:44,320
Can you find that previous tenant
and arrange a meeting for me?

776
00:58:45,000 --> 00:58:46,090
Why?

777
00:58:46,120 --> 00:58:48,105
I wanna talk to her.

778
00:58:48,135 --> 00:58:50,120
Ask her why she did this

779
00:58:50,150 --> 00:58:51,040
Did what?

780
00:58:51,440 --> 00:58:53,090
Did what?

781
00:58:53,120 --> 00:58:55,760
Sent this thug to our house

782
00:58:55,790 --> 00:58:56,850
Why would she do that?

783
00:58:56,880 --> 00:59:00,640
