about us touching her stuff.

784
00:59:00,670 --> 00:59:03,379
She's nothing like that.
She hasn't taken her stuff

785
00:59:03,409 --> 00:59:05,600
because she still
hasn't found a place.

786
00:59:05,601 --> 00:59:08,101
