with me that day.

787
00:59:09,120 --> 00:59:10,240
Hello

788
00:59:11,200 --> 00:59:12,810
Feeling better?

789
00:59:12,840 --> 00:59:14,880
Yep, I'm fine thanks

790
00:59:23,120 --> 00:59:25,200
Did you tell the guys?

791
00:59:25,560 --> 00:59:26,250
No

792
00:59:26,280 --> 00:59:27,850
Then how do they know?

793
00:59:27,880 --> 00:59:30,560
One of the neighbor had called Babak.

794
00:59:30,590 --> 00:59:32,400
I'm not sure what they said

795
00:59:33,440 --> 00:59:36,140
Emad, get dressed and
come for the make up.

796
00:59:39,040 --> 00:59:40,960
My outfit's not here

797
00:59:41,480 --> 00:59:43,920
Kati's going to take your place tonight.

798
00:59:53,960 --> 00:59:55,945
