It's not up to me.

800
00:59:58,080 --> 01:00:01,130
The director wanted her
to replace you tonight.

801
01:00:01,160 --> 01:00:04,520
If you're alright, and you can do it,
I'll go talk to her.

802
01:00:04,550 --> 01:00:06,200
No, I don't want to

803
01:00:07,120 --> 01:00:09,280
Have you started house-hunting?

804
01:00:10,040 --> 01:00:11,760
No, I will do

805
01:00:13,200 --> 01:00:14,330
