806
01:00:14,360 --> 01:00:17,960
When you get time! Like it doesn't
matter how I feel in that place!

807
01:00:17,990 --> 01:00:19,440
You haven't done anything

808
01:00:19,470 --> 01:00:20,880
Huh?

809
01:00:22,560 --> 01:00:25,330
