812
01:00:38,840 --> 01:00:39,840
Auntie?

813
01:00:40,280 --> 01:00:41,810
Yes Baby?

814
01:00:41,840 --> 01:00:44,560
Why aren't you acting tonight?

815
01:00:45,240 --> 01:00:47,400
I'm not feeling well tonight, darling.

816
01:00:47,430 --> 01:00:49,720
Why did you come here then?

817
01:00:49,750 --> 01:00:52,040
I get bored at home

818
01:00:52,070 --> 01:00:53,490
What?

819
01:00:53,520 --> 01:00:55,880
I get bored at home

820
01:00:56,480 --> 01:01:01,400
Well, I get bored here.

821
01:01:03,520 --> 01:01:06,400
Would you like to come
to our house this evening?

822
01:01:06,760 --> 01:01:08,770
Do you have Spongebob?

823
01:01:08,800 --> 01:01:11,010
No, but we can go buy it on the way home.

824
01:01:11,040 --> 01:01:13,570
