need to perform again.

825
01:01:13,600 --> 01:01:17,800
Everything's Topsy turvy.
Everybody's making mistakes.

826
01:01:19,000 --> 01:01:20,210
Why?

827
01:01:20,240 --> 01:01:22,210
I don't know, everyone's upset

828
01:01:22,240 --> 01:01:24,640
You're better now,
