829
01:01:24,670 --> 01:01:25,340
Mum?

830
01:01:25,370 --> 01:01:26,010
Darling?

831
01:01:26,040 --> 01:01:27,160
Can I go to Auntie's house?

832
01:01:27,190 --> 01:01:28,050
No, baby.

833
01:01:28,080 --> 01:01:32,935
Let him stay with me tonight, I'm alone.
I'll bring him with me tomorrow.

834
01:01:32,965 --> 01:01:37,820
