848
01:02:27,630 --> 01:02:28,800
Where did he go?

849
01:02:28,830 --> 01:02:29,570
Huh?

850
01:02:29,600 --> 01:02:31,280
Where'd he go?

851
01:02:31,720 --> 01:02:34,200
