863
01:03:04,520 --> 01:03:06,040
Are you feeling shy in front of me?

864
01:03:06,070 --> 01:03:06,920
Nope!

865
01:03:08,320 --> 01:03:09,840
Can you do it yourself?

866
01:03:30,440 --> 01:03:32,800
I'm drawing his mustache

867
01:03:41,720 --> 01:03:42,840
Yes?

868
01:03:43,560 --> 01:03:44,800
Come up, dear.

869
01:03:45,240 --> 01:03:46,560
Who was it?

870
01:03:47,280 --> 01:03:48,530
Uncle Emad

871
01:03:48,560 --> 01:03:52,480
If it's my dad,
then tell him Sadra's not here.

872
01:03:52,510 --> 01:03:53,600
Why?

873
01:03:54,840 --> 01:03:57,040
Because I love my Mom

874
01:03:57,070 --> 01:03:58,120
Okay

875
01:04:11,800 --> 01:04:12,960
Rana?

876
01:04:13,200 --> 01:04:13,770
Hey

877
01:04:13,800 --> 01:04:15,665
The pickup isn't in the parking.

878
01:04:15,695 --> 01:04:17,560
I parked it outside this morning.

879
01:04:17,590 --> 01:04:19,130
Why?

880
01:04:19,160 --> 01:04:22,680
I didn't fancy moving
it every ten minutes

881
01:04:22,710 --> 01:04:23,570
Hello!

882
01:04:23,600 --> 01:04:26,480
Helloooo, how are you kid?

883
01:04:26,510 --> 01:04:27,940
Where are the keys?

884
01:04:27,970 --> 01:04:29,400
Where you'd left them.

885
01:04:30,480 --> 01:04:32,265
How are things with my favorite?

886
01:04:32,295 --> 01:04:34,080
Welcome to our house, all good?

887
01:04:34,520 --> 01:04:35,680
Welcome!

888
01:04:39,960 --> 01:04:41,960
Leave it where it is Emad

889
01:04:41,990 --> 01:04:43,360
I'll be right back

890
01:04:43,390 --> 01:04:44,760
Emad... Emad...

891
01:04:46,760 --> 01:04:49,865
Let's forget all that for tonight,
just leave it.

892
01:04:49,895 --> 01:04:53,000
I've made dinner,
go wash your hands and change.

893
01:04:53,440 --> 01:04:54,720
Go on, darling

894
01:05:05,800 --> 01:05:09,120
Ready for takeoff
ladies and gentleman!

895
01:05:12,800 --> 01:05:14,520
Sadra!

896
01:05:14,920 --> 01:05:15,970
Yes!

897
01:05:16,000 --> 01:05:18,000
Emad it's ready,
come before it gets cold.

898
01:05:18,030 --> 01:05:19,200
Coming

899
01:05:19,480 --> 01:05:21,200
Let's go wash those hands of yours.

900
01:05:21,230 --> 01:05:22,850
My hands are clean!

901
01:05:22,880 --> 01:05:25,145
Let's wash them again anyways.

902
01:05:25,175 --> 01:05:27,440
Wow, wow, wow, look at this!

903
01:05:29,000 --> 01:05:31,040
Thanks so much

904
01:05:33,560 --> 01:05:34,530
Get your hands off it!

905
01:05:34,560 --> 01:05:38,650
<i>Rana, where are you?</i>

906
01:05:38,680 --> 01:05:41,320
<i>Sadra, come and eat!</i>

907
01:05:41,920 --> 01:05:44,330
Helllllo

908
01:05:44,360 --> 01:05:48,080
Hello trouble, have you two been
having fun without me?

909
01:05:48,110 --> 01:05:48,410
We went shopping
and then hung out

910
01:05:48,440 --> 01:05:49,960
Well done!
We went shopping and then hung out

911
01:05:49,990 --> 01:05:51,520
We went shopping and then hung out

912
01:05:51,720 --> 01:05:54,160
But we didn't find Spongebob

913
01:05:54,190 --> 01:05:56,130
Yes, unfortunately.

914
01:05:56,160 --> 01:05:58,947
<i>Don't worry, Patrick,
eventually a good day will come</i>

915
01:05:58,977 --> 01:06:00,800
<i>when you and I will find someone.</i>

916
01:06:01,400 --> 01:06:04,880
<i>Look at this, Spongebob!</i>

917
01:06:05,400 --> 01:06:09,000
Look what Auntie Rana made, macaroni!

918
01:06:10,920 --> 01:06:11,770
More?

919
01:06:11,800 --> 01:06:13,120
No no, that's enough

920
01:06:13,520 --> 01:06:15,280
Okay, just let me know

921
01:06:15,310 --> 01:06:17,080
Thank you

922
01:06:19,240 --> 01:06:22,360
Wow, what a nice macaroni!

923
01:06:22,390 --> 01:06:23,840
Bon appetit!

924
01:06:23,870 --> 01:06:25,320
Let's eat it all

925
01:06:25,600 --> 01:06:27,120
Look what she's made.

926
01:06:27,150 --> 01:06:28,320
Yeah, I know!

927
01:06:29,720 --> 01:06:31,440
How was tonight's performance?

928
01:06:32,280 --> 01:06:33,680
Very...

929
01:06:34,120 --> 01:06:35,280
not that great.

930
01:06:35,520 --> 01:06:36,845
It was terrible

931
01:06:36,875 --> 01:06:38,170
You're lying

932
01:06:38,200 --> 01:06:40,480
That's how it is without you

933
01:06:42,280 --> 01:06:43,760
Did you find the credit card?

934
01:06:43,790 --> 01:06:45,120
No

935
01:06:47,400 --> 01:06:48,760
How did you go shopping?

936
01:06:49,120 --> 01:06:50,880
With the money you'd left

937
01:06:52,200 --> 01:06:53,485
What money?

938
01:06:53,515 --> 01:06:54,800
In the drawer.

939
01:07:09,400 --> 01:07:11,440
Why aren't you eating?
Do you not like it?

940
01:07:11,880 --> 01:07:14,280
Is it not tasty?

941
01:07:23,000 --> 01:07:24,760
Don't eat it

942
01:07:26,440 --> 01:07:27,600
What's up?

943
01:07:36,520 --> 01:07:39,360
That scumbag had left it behind
the other night.

944
01:08:05,920 --> 01:08:07,280
Sadra?

945
01:08:08,440 --> 01:08:10,280
I've got an idea

946
01:08:10,640 --> 01:08:11,760
Do you like pizza?

947
01:08:11,790 --> 01:08:12,720
Yep

948
01:08:13,480 --> 01:08:15,000
Then let's order some pizza.

949
01:08:15,240 --> 01:08:17,160
Don't eat that, it's not good

950
01:08:19,680 --> 01:08:21,520
Do you like fries?

951
01:08:22,400 --> 01:08:24,200
And after that Ice Cream?

952
01:08:34,101 --> 01:08:34,901
Hi there.
Gimme a call when you can.

953
01:08:35,120 --> 01:08:39,000
Hello? Mum? Mummy?

954
01:08:41,080 --> 01:08:44,880
Hello? Uncle?
Are you there?

955
01:08:46,080 --> 01:08:49,840
It's the 3rd time I'm calling.

956
01:08:51,320 --> 01:08:53,160
Ahoo darling, it's Babak

957
01:08:55,320 --> 01:08:59,680
Ahoo... Ahoo...

958
01:09:00,760 --> 01:09:02,880
Are you there?

959
01:09:07,360 --> 01:09:12,760
Gimme a call when you get home,
I'll be up late.

960
01:09:15,960 --> 01:09:17,840
What are you doing?

961
01:09:18,880 --> 01:09:20,320
Nothing

962
01:09:20,840 --> 01:09:22,360
Come on, go sleep.

963
01:09:22,680 --> 01:09:24,400
You haven't slept for two nights

964
01:09:24,560 --> 01:09:26,480
I can't sleep.

965
01:09:34,080 --> 01:09:36,480
Why did you open her letters?

966
01:09:36,510 --> 01:09:37,890
It's her private stuff.

967
01:09:37,920 --> 01:09:39,800
I wanna find out
who the hell that scumbag was.

968
01:09:39,830 --> 01:09:42,020
Let's say you find out how it was...

969
01:09:42,560 --> 01:09:44,045
He'll say it was a mistake

970
01:09:44,075 --> 01:09:45,530
He came inside by mistake?

971
01:09:45,560 --> 01:09:47,970
He rang the bell
and I opened the door.

972
01:09:48,000 --> 01:09:51,440
He must've thought it's that woman
since I opened the door so easily.

973
01:09:51,470 --> 01:09:52,600
He came here by mistake?

974
01:09:52,920 --> 01:09:55,040
Any when he realized his mistake...

975
01:09:55,070 --> 01:09:56,730
...Why didn't he leave?

976
01:09:56,760 --> 01:09:59,520
Because he saw the bathroom light's on
and there's a woman in there?

977
01:09:59,550 --> 01:10:01,180
How would he know it's a...

978
01:10:01,210 --> 01:10:02,840
From your clothes on the bed.

979
01:10:05,800 --> 01:10:08,600
If I'd just used the damn intercom...

980
01:10:08,630 --> 01:10:11,120
If I'd just asked who it was...

981
01:10:11,880 --> 01:10:13,800
None of this would've happened

982
01:10:13,900 --> 01:10:15,890
If you think it's that simple...

983
01:10:15,920 --> 01:10:19,800
You can just tell all the neighbors
about the intercom...

984
01:10:19,900 --> 01:10:21,535
Why are you getting
the neighbors into this?

985
01:10:21,565 --> 01:10:23,347
They knew what was
going on in this house.

986
01:10:23,377 --> 01:10:25,160
So it'd be fine with you,
if they didn't know?

987
01:10:25,190 --> 01:10:27,160
What are you on about?

988
01:10:28,661 --> 01:10:29,861
Leave me alone.

989
01:10:45,080 --> 01:10:46,880
The pickup wasn't there

990
01:10:46,910 --> 01:10:47,520
What?

991
01:10:49,480 --> 01:10:50,360
Sorry

992
01:10:51,880 --> 01:10:53,040
Where was it?

993
01:10:53,640 --> 01:10:54,805
There

994
01:10:54,835 --> 01:10:56,000
Sorry

995
01:10:59,560 --> 01:11:00,760
Where did you leave it?

996
01:11:00,790 --> 01:11:01,960
I left it there

997
01:11:05,000 --> 01:11:05,680
Where?

998
01:11:05,800 --> 01:11:08,360
Over there, where the Peugeot is

999
01:11:15,320 --> 01:11:16,640
He's taken it

1000
01:11:18,000 --> 01:11:19,880
I have to find that asshole

1001
01:11:36,800 --> 01:11:38,560
Jackass!

1002
01:11:44,360 --> 01:11:46,240
Okay, slow down!

1003
01:12:12,000 --> 01:12:13,360
It's freezing in there.

1004
01:12:13,520 --> 01:12:14,410
Never mind.

1005
01:12:14,440 --> 01:12:16,640
What do you mean, never mind?
You'll get sick.

1006
01:12:16,670 --> 01:12:17,730
Let's go to a public bath.

1007
01:12:17,760 --> 01:12:20,160
No, I'll be out quick.
Just wait here.

1008
01:12:29,640 --> 01:12:31,120
Hasanpoor, come here a sec.

1009
01:12:31,150 --> 01:12:32,880
<i>Hello</i>

1010
01:12:39,600 --> 01:12:40,920
What can I do for you, Sir?

1011
01:12:40,950 --> 01:12:41,770
Hi

1012
01:12:41,800 --> 01:12:43,800
How's it going?

1013
01:12:44,080 --> 01:12:46,200
Your dad was a traffic cop, right?

1014
01:12:46,230 --> 01:12:47,680
